title: Renovated 2 bedroom 1 bath with upgraded appliances and high ceilings
posting_body: ['Welcome to The Colonnade Apartments!', 'CALL:', 'show contact info', '$2,926 - $3,615', '.', '2 Bed 1 Bath .', '1000 Sq.Ft', '* Unit 523 - Available 08/06/22', '* Unit 604 - Available 09/08/22', 'The Colonnade Apartments', 'Address:', '201 S 4th Street San Jose, CA 95112', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Choose this two-bedroom, one-bathroom model and make The Colonnade Apartments your new home.', 'This spacious model features in-wall USB ports, so you’ll have a convenient way to charge electronic devices.', 'You can enjoy calming views as you relax on your private balcony.', 'Prepare quick meals in the galley kitchen with quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast bar.', 'Interior elements such as vinyl plank flooring and multi-panel doors add style and beauty to the interior.', 'Make the most out of the community amenities such as the fitness center, the clubhouse, and the laundry room.', 'After a long day, take a refreshing soak in the Jacuzzi or the swimming pool.', 'You can also visit the sauna for a different type of relaxation.', 'Explore all these at The Colonnade Apartments!', 'Call now!', 'OFFICE\u2002 \u2002HOURS', 'Monday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Tuesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Wednesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Thursday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Friday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Saturday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Sunday', 'Closed', 'CALL US TODAY!', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
